function missionHelp()
  trigger.action.outText("Missions are seperated into two catagories, 'Rescue' and 'Search & Rescue', these have 3 levels of difficulties to choose from.\n\nRescue missions will give you the grid and lat long coordinates that you fly to and pickup the patient. When you are within 5 Nautical Miles of the area you can ask for a Flare.\n\nSearch & Rescue missions will give you a description of the area or a grid location the indavidual or group is lost. Fly to the area and search for the indavidual or group and rescue them.\n\nOnce you have your Patient(s) on board, fly them to one of the hospitals in the area. These are marked on your map.", 60)
end

